Package com.amazonaws.mobileconnectors.pinpoint.analytics

Class Session

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amazonaws.mobileconnectors.pinpoint.analytics.Session
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JSONSerializable
    public class Session
extends java.lang.Object
implements JSONSerializable
    A Session Object Mostly immutable, with the exception of its stop time. This session object tracks whether or not it has been paused by checking the status of it's stop time. A session's stop time is only set when the session has been paused, and is set to -1 if it is currently running. Can be serialized and restored for persistence.
